<section id="design-service-header" class="container-fluid m-0 p-0">
    <div class="design-services-poly1">
        <h1>DESIGN</h1>
        <blockquote class="design-services-poly1-quote">"Design is not just what it looks like and feels like.<br />Design is how it works."</blockquote>
        <div class="design-services-poly1-quote-author">Steve Jobs</div>
    </div>

</section>

@*/******************************************/
    /* Design Service Intro Text              */
    /******************************************/*@

<section id="design-service-intro" class="container-fluid m-0 p-0" data-aos="fade-up" data-aos-duration="1500">
    <div class="design-services-introbox">
        <div class="design-services-introbox-title">
            Start with the end in mind
        </div>
        <div class="design-services-introbox-text">
            If you need a new web site or are thinking about revamping your existing site where is the best place to start? What is the best way to create a compelling website which will maximise your appeal to potential customers?
            At Adcreo we use a three step approach to firstly focus on understanding your target customers then, through prototyping, explore different ideas and concepts and finally jointly agree a “blueprint”, an agreed way forwward to build
            (or update) your website and keep it in tip-top condition.
        </div>
    </div>
</section>

@*/******************************************/
    /* Design Service Design Service Cards    */
    /******************************************/*@

<section id="design-service-cards" class="container-fluid m-0 p-0" data-aos="fade-up" data-aos-duration="1500">
    <div class="card-group design-card-group" >
        <div class="card">
            <img class="card-img-top design-card-image-size" src="~/Media/iStock-503465634-cust-analysis.jpg" alt="Customer Requirements Analysis" />
            <div class="card-block">
                <h4 class="card-title design-card-title">INSIGHT</h4>
                <p class="card-text">
                    We listen to you to get an understanding of your business, objectives , opportunities and challenges.  We use various techniques to probe (and challenge) to define a clear problem
                    or opportunity statement which provides focus and context to inform future decisions. We create “customer journeys” and examine your potential customer touchpoints – and how to
                    measure and maximise your impact at each one.
                </p>
            </div>
        </div>
        <div class="card">
            <img class="card-img-top design-card-image-size" src="~/Media/iStock-511658830.jpg" alt="Card image cap">
            <div class="card-block">
                <h4 class="card-title design-card-title">EXPLORE</h4>
                <p class="card-text">
                    We use variety of techniques, such as mood boards and wireframe mock-ups to test and validate the look and feel of your website.
                    We iterate and refine then draft what eventually becomes the input to the Blueprint phase.
                </p>
            </div>
        </div>
        <div class="card">
            <img class="card-img-top design-card-image-size" src="~/Media/iStock-547130486.jpg" alt="Card image cap">
            <div class="card-block">
                <h4 class="card-title design-card-title">BLUEPRINT</h4>
                <p class="card-text">
                    We take the output of the Explore phase and turn this into a transformation plan.  This plan considers the scope of work to be carried out by Adcreo and our on-going role to support you.
                    It also considers any organisational and process recommendations we may have for your company to, ensuring you have the best opportunity to align your way of working to the new website and the impact it will have on our business.
                </p>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</section>

